{"tid":1984617,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"THE 泰晤士大學影響力排行榜 嶺大首參與 港大暴跌31位至41位","createTime":"2020-04-22T14:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T23:10:36.000Z","uid":51200,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b8fbe876b529d9f060c5b33adf910223ca67683","tid":1984617,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:37:36.000Z","msg":"英國《泰晤士報高等教育特刊》(THE)今(22日)公布2020年大學影響力排名，本港多間大學排名下跌。其中去年躋身綜合排名第10位的香港大學今年跌至第41位，但仍是本港唯一一間排名前100位的大學，至於去年第60名的香港浸會大學亦跌至100位後。不過，在多個細項中，港大在「和平、正義及強大機構」一項勇奪亞軍，而嶺南大學亦在「優質教育」一項名列世界第2位。<br />\n<br />\n該排名是按聯合國17個可持續發展目標（SDG）作衡量標準，以比較全球大學在社會影響力的表現，今年有89個國家、逾850間大學參與評估，較去年增加301間。本港院校僅港大成功躋身前百位，排行第41，較去年下跌31位，該校在「和平、正義及強大機構」方面仍然排行全球第2位，該排名以參與政府顧問工作及學術自由政策等方面表現為依據。<br />\n<br />\n嶺南大學則在「優質教育」方面排行世界第2位，該校稱其綜合排名約為第101至200位，但在「無貧窮」及「體面工作和經濟增長」方面分別獲第48位及第71位。該校校長鄭國漢稱對排名感歡迎，證明嶺大在優質教育的承諾和貢獻獲國際學術界認可。<br />\n<br />\n港大回應指，該排名有別於其他的學術排名，影響力排名着眼於大學對社會和經濟所發揮的影響力，以及對政府、商業社會以及廣大群眾帶來的正面意義。該校指在大部分細項分數都有所提高，尤其有一分項排名全球第2。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200422/bkn-20200422190937459-0422_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200422%2Fbkn-20200422190937459-0422_00822_001.html&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CphvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=859599ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200422/bkn-20200422190937459-0422_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e86a501974e074c5622456d0fd34c4a89b6663b4","tid":1984617,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"THE Impact Rankings 2019<br />\nThe Times Higher Education Impact Rankings are the only global performance tables that assess universities against the United Nations&rsquo; Sustainable Development Goals. We use carefully calibrated indicators to provide comprehensive and balanced comparisons across three broad areas: research, outreach, and stewardship.<br />\n<br />\nThis first edition includes more than 450 universities from 76 countries.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.timeshighereducation.com/rankings/impact/2019/overall#!/page/0/length/25/sort_by/rank/sort_order/asc/cols/undefined\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timeshighereducation.com%2Frankings%2Fimpact%2F2019%2Foverall%23%21%2Fpage%2F0%2Flength%2F25%2Fsort_by%2Frank%2Fsort_order%2Fasc%2Fcols%2Fundefined&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CphvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=0feed898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.timeshighereducation.com/rankings/impact/2019/overall#!/page/0/length/25/sort_by/rank/sort_order/asc/cols/undefined</a><br />\n<br />\nWhat the fuck is it?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f87fc94e94e6bbcaabe7bb7eb251215ae5d174","tid":1984617,"uid":51200,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:41:51.000Z","msg":"該校在「和平、正義及強大機構」方面仍然排行全球第2位<br />\n<br />\nHKU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4ed8803519da2fcaad528640b5e7d445169aa4","tid":1984617,"uid":102835,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:44:03.000Z","msg":"跌極個紅底校長咪又係不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef2dce565b3e73879a44babd00acb7e6be74bd4","tid":1984617,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c4ed8803519da2fcaad528640b5e7d445169aa4","tid":1984617,"uid":102835,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14: